{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b52201f6d5","title":"在陈嘉庚来信上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c3781799a7","index":0,"year":1955,"month":11,"day":1,"articleId":"b52201f6d5"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"1a0629ef09","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"b52201f6d5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈嘉庚，当时任全国人大常委会委员、政协全国委员会副主席。"},{"id":"509827470c","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"b52201f6d5","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指陈嘉庚1955年10月9日给毛泽东的信。信中说，我此次访问西北，于9月中旬再访延安，途经黄陵县时，顺便拜遇黄帝陵和轩转庙，院中历代碑石犹在，千年古柏森森。惟庙宇木料多已腐坏，势将倾璃，庭中草地，多为农民耕种，陵山多处私垃如鳞。曾查询县长，据说自解放后至今未派人看管。保护山陵标语虽有，但徒有其名。黄帝陵乃我国民族历史遗迹，解放后人民政府对历史文物及各处寺庙尚且保护修饰，而黄帝陵庙竟任荒废，抑或中央主管部门因偏鲜未暇顾及。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d2b269dfaf","type":"title","text":"在陈嘉庚来信上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"b52201f6d5"},{"id":"1a0629ef09","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"b52201f6d5"},{"id":"509827470c","type":"paragraph","text":"此件回阅后，请批交有关机关处理。我看陈先生的提议是有道理的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"b52201f6d5"},{"id":"b95836f7c2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"b52201f6d5"},{"id":"251655dd0e","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"b52201f6d5"}],"page":{"id":"d4457c880a","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"b52201f6d5","start":53,"end":53}}}},"__N_SSG":true}